\s1 Exposition of Psalm 95: Hearing God’s Word in Faith
\p 
\v 7 \w Therefore|strong="G1352"\w*, \w as|strong="G2531"\w* \w the|strong="G3588"\w* \w Holy|strong="G4151"\w* \w Spirit|strong="G4151"\w* \w says|strong="G3004"\w*,
\q1 “\qt Oh, that today you would listen as he speaks!\qt*
\q1 
