\q1 
\v 9 “\qt There your fathers tested me and tried me, and they saw my works for forty years\qt*.
\q1 
\v 10 “\qt Therefore, I became provoked at that generation and said, ‘Their hearts are always wandering and they have not known my ways\qt*.’
\q1 
